{"tid":2048591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Boris Johnson: 英國唔會妨礙中國崛起","createTime":"2020-06-03T02:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T05:03:02.000Z","uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"690a67e2ff330769bba5b0d5a36fe752d57e6823","tid":2048591,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"全國人大上周通過「港版國安法」，英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）今日（3日）於香港《南華早報》發表文章，若港版國安法一旦正式實施，英國已準備好延長持有英國國民海外護照（BNO）的港人到英國的簽證至12個月，並進一步給予移民權利，包括於當地工作。他形容，假如落實修改簽證制定，將是英國史上，其中一個最大的移民政策修訂（one of the biggest changes in our visa system in British history）。<br />\n<br />\n他同時希望中國與國際合作，讓香港繼續繁榮發展，又強調英國並不打算妨礙中國崛起，相反希望雙方可在各個議題合作，並歡迎中國成為國際領袖之一，期望中國會遵守國際協議。<br />\n<br />\nSource：China01"},{"pid":"927d8a8e991b55ae23175a267c928ebd2a05ecee","tid":2048591,"uid":144626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"即係話, 去到英國都未必有運行<br />\n香港人仍然會活喺支那陰影之下<br />\n隨時俾當地支那人欺壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f2dc9383d21107d6296251506339630a7bfe89","tid":2048591,"uid":55955,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:15:35.000Z","msg":"期望中國會遵守國際協議<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30890c2ee68ae80e567fe497b371d2d7386bd26","tid":2048591,"uid":103230,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:19:24.000Z","msg":"英國的確冇本錢同中国硬撼<br />\n都係個句唔使旨意歐洲出手架喇<br />\n班舊世界昔日列強殘晒"},{"pid":"b9826ebe9f18bd7f9a6eb5b3ced2a5a213d5aa3b","tid":2048591,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a30890c2ee68ae80e567fe497b371d2d7386bd26","tid":2